&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/609&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/609&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-1851&quot; title=&quot;OffsetFetchRequest returns extra partitions when input only contains unknown partitions&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-1851&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-1851&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; Using random dir under /temp for local kdc files to avoid conflicts.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    when multiple test jobs are running.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    I manually separated changes for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-2851&quot; title=&quot;system tests: error copying keytab file&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-2851&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-2851&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; from this PR:  &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/570&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/570&lt;/a&gt; which also had &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-2825&quot; title=&quot;Add controller failover to existing replication tests&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-2825&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-2825&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; changes.&lt;/p&gt;

