&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;commit d19a8533243a77f026a4f547bad40fd10dd68745&lt;br/&gt;
Author: Anna Povzner &amp;lt;anna@confluent.io&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
